---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import StructuredData from '../components/StructuredData.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Case Studies | Start & Scale Growth Advisory"
	description="Real outcomes from real engagements. Revenue builds, tech modernization, and full-stack platform development for founder-led companies."
	canonical="/case-studies"
>
	<StructuredData type="organization" />

	<!-- Hero -->
			<section class="bg-dark pt-32 pb-16 sm:pt-40 sm:pb-20 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-28">
				<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
					<h1 class="font-display text-white text-h1 lg:text-[3.75rem] lg:leading-[1.05] max-w-4xl">
						The work.
					</h1>
					<p class="text-body-lg text-body-light mt-6 max-w-2xl">
						Every engagement starts the same way: a company that outgrew its infrastructure needs a team that can build the solution and run it. Here's what that looks like.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Case Study 1: National Nonprofit -->
			<section class="bg-background py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
				<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
					<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
						<div class="lg:col-span-4">
							<p class="text-small text-accent uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">National Nonprofit</p>
							<p class="font-display text-accent text-stat lg:text-[4.5rem] lg:leading-none">29</p>
							<p class="text-small text-body mt-1">states, one system</p>
							<div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
								<span class="text-small text-body bg-surface px-3 py-1 rounded">Operations & Systems</span>
								<span class="text-small text-body bg-surface px-3 py-1 rounded">Fundraising</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="lg:col-span-8">
							<h2 class="font-display text-headline text-h3">Fundraising & technology modernization for a 15-year-old organization</h2>
							<div class="mt-8">
								<h3 class="font-display text-headline text-h4">Challenge</h3>
								<p class="text-body text-body mt-3">
									A national nonprofit had grown to operate across 29 states, but its infrastructure hadn't kept pace. Donor data lived in spreadsheets and inboxes. The team ran fundraising by hand. There was no centralized system for tracking relationships, campaigns, or outcomes.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div class="mt-8">
								<h3 class="font-display text-headline text-h4">Approach</h3>
								<p class="text-body text-body mt-3">
									Implemented Salesforce NPSP as the central donor management platform. Built email campaigns in Salesforce Marketing Cloud. Integrated GA4 and Givebutter for digital fundraising tracking. Developed grant writing processes and a donor stewardship strategy that connected online engagement to offline relationship management.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div class="mt-8">
								<h3 class="font-display text-headline text-h4">Outcomes</h3>
								<ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
									<li class="text-body text-body pl-4 border-l-2 border-accent">Centralized donor data for a 29-state operation into a single CRM</li>
									<li class="text-body text-body pl-4 border-l-2 border-accent">Launched first digital fundraising campaigns with end-to-end tracking</li>
									<li class="text-body text-body pl-4 border-l-2 border-accent">Connected marketing analytics (GA4) to donor management (Salesforce)</li>
									<li class="text-body text-body pl-4 border-l-2 border-accent">Built repeatable grant writing and stewardship workflows</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Divider -->
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8"><hr class="border-border" /></div>

			<!-- Case Study 2: Off-Grid Education Startup -->
			<section class="bg-background py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
				<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
					<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
						<div class="lg:col-span-4">
							<p class="text-small text-accent uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Off-Grid Education Startup</p>
							<p class="font-display text-accent text-stat lg:text-[4.5rem] lg:leading-none">0→1</p>
							<p class="text-small text-body mt-1">market-ready</p>
							<div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
								<span class="text-small text-body bg-surface px-3 py-1 rounded">Revenue & GTM</span>
								<span class="text-small text-body bg-surface px-3 py-1 rounded">AI & Automation</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="lg:col-span-8">
							<h2 class="font-display text-headline text-h3">GTM and content strategy for a new entrant in a niche market</h2>
							<div class="mt-8">
								<h3 class="font-display text-headline text-h4">Challenge</h3>
								<p class="text-body text-body mt-3">
									A new company entering the outdoor education and preparedness space had no audience, no brand presence, and no revenue infrastructure. The founder had deep subject-matter expertise but no GTM playbook.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div class="mt-8">
								<h3 class="font-display text-headline text-h4">Approach</h3>
								<p class="text-body text-body mt-3">
									Defined brand positioning and competitive differentiation. Built the content strategy and editorial calendar. Configured AI-powered marketing agents for content production. Developed the pricing model and validated it against the market.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div class="mt-8">
								<h3 class="font-display text-headline text-h4">Outcomes</h3>
								<ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
									<li class="text-body text-body pl-4 border-l-2 border-accent">Complete marketing infrastructure built from scratch</li>
									<li class="text-body text-body pl-4 border-l-2 border-accent">Brand voice and positioning defined, content calendar populated</li>
									<li class="text-body text-body pl-4 border-l-2 border-accent">AI marketing agents configured and producing content</li>
									<li class="text-body text-body pl-4 border-l-2 border-accent">Pricing model validated and launched</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Divider -->
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8"><hr class="border-border" /></div>

			<!-- Case Study 3: Legal-Tech SaaS -->
			<section class="bg-background py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
				<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
					<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
						<div class="lg:col-span-4">
							<p class="text-small text-accent uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Legal-Tech SaaS Platform</p>
							<p class="font-display text-accent text-stat lg:text-[4.5rem] lg:leading-none">19</p>
							<p class="text-small text-body mt-1">Edge Functions, one engineer</p>
							<div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
								<span class="text-small text-body bg-surface px-3 py-1 rounded">Operations & Systems</span>
								<span class="text-small text-body bg-surface px-3 py-1 rounded">AI & Automation</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="lg:col-span-8">
							<h2 class="font-display text-headline text-h3">Full-stack platform build in a complex regulatory domain</h2>
							<div class="mt-8">
								<h3 class="font-display text-headline text-h4">Challenge</h3>
								<p class="text-body text-body mt-3">
									A complex regulatory domain (irrevocable life insurance trust administration) needed an end-to-end software platform. No existing product served the market. The build required document processing, compliance workflows, role-based access, and AI integration. There was no engineering team.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div class="mt-8">
								<h3 class="font-display text-headline text-h4">Approach</h3>
								<p class="text-body text-body mt-3">
									Designed and built the entire platform: React frontend, TypeScript backend, Supabase database and auth, 19 Supabase Edge Functions, AI document processing via Gemini, automated PDF generation, and a full role-based permission system.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div class="mt-8">
								<h3 class="font-display text-headline text-h4">Outcomes</h3>
								<ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
									<li class="text-body text-body pl-4 border-l-2 border-accent">V1 shipped: end-to-end tested, production-ready</li>
									<li class="text-body text-body pl-4 border-l-2 border-accent">19 Edge Functions handling business logic, document processing, and integrations</li>
									<li class="text-body text-body pl-4 border-l-2 border-accent">AI-powered document intake and data extraction</li>
									<li class="text-body text-body pl-4 border-l-2 border-accent">Full authentication and role-based access control</li>
									<li class="text-body text-body pl-4 border-l-2 border-accent">Zero external engineering resources</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- CTA Block -->
			<section class="bg-dark py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24">
				<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 text-center">
					<h2 class="font-display text-white text-h2 lg:text-[3rem] lg:leading-[1.1]">Your company could be next.</h2>
					<p class="text-body-lg text-body-light mt-4 max-w-xl mx-auto">30 minutes. We'll listen to where you are, and if we can help, we'll tell you exactly how.</p>
					<div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 items-center">
						<a href="https://calendly.com/chris-ssgrowthadvisors/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-accent text-white text-btn px-7 py-3.5 rounded hover:bg-accent-hover transition-colors duration-150 cursor-pointer inline-block">
							Book a Call
						</a>
						<a href="/contact" class="text-body-light text-btn hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150 cursor-pointer inline-block py-3.5">
							Or send a message &rarr;
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
</BaseLayout>
